OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775578269
OL,3,CMan charged in connection with murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation in Weston-super-Mare
OL,6,FA man has been charged in connection
OL,7,Fwith a murder investigation in Weston-
OL,8,Fsuper-Mare.
OL,10,FRichard Woolley, 58, from Birmingham,
OL,11,Fhas been charged with one count of
OL,12,Fmurder and has been remanded in
OL,13,Fcustody. He will appear at North
OL,14,FSomerset Magistrates' Court on Tuesday
OL,15,F7 May.
OL,17,FIt comes after a man was found dead at
OL,18,Fan address in Eagle Close on Saturday
OL,19,F4 April.
