OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775578269
OL,3,CMan charged in connection with murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation in Weston-super-Mare
OL,6,FThe next of kin of the deceased has
OL,7,Fbeen informed and Avon and Somerset
OL,8,FPolice is in contact with them.
OL,10,FDI Alan Smith, Senior Investigating
OL,11,FOfficer for Avon and Somerset Police's
OL,12,FMajor Crime Investigation Team, said:
OL,13,F"We were called by the ambulance
OL,14,Fservice after paramedics found a man
OL,15,Ftragically deceased at an address in
OL,16,FWeston-super-Mare on Saturday evening.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
