OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775578269
OL,3,CMan charged in connection with murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation in Weston-super-Mare
OL,6,F"We have charged a 58-year-old man who
OL,7,Fis known to the deceased, and we
OL,8,Fremain in contact with his family. We
OL,9,Fare not looking for anybody else in
OL,10,Fconnection with this investigation,
OL,11,Fwhich will continue.
OL,13,F"Officers will maintain a presence in
OL,14,Fthe area over coming days, and anybody
OL,15,Fwith concerns are encouraged to speak
OL,16,Fto them."
